{"tid":669422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦：如果真係有得畀我揀的話，我會選擇留喺呢度。","createTime":"2018-05-18T12:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T19:06:52.000Z","uid":5843,"like":154,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2021dda6738602185ae623167a3997604161cd53","tid":669422,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"【不要讓每一個抵抗爭者孤單】<br />\n<br />\n「如果真係有得畀我揀的話，我會選擇留喺呢度。因為香港過往冇出現過一啲願意為自己政治理念犧牲咁多嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n過往好多人都話香港想有改變呀？想有民主呀？或者好似而家咁想獨立呀？都冇人去搞啦，冇人肯同你癲啦，冇人肯犧牲啦，個個都睇死香港，冇人敢咁樣去做。<br />\n<br />\n所以我一定會選擇留低，因為我要證明香港係有人，願意為佢嘅政治理念，完全獻身。」<br />\n<br />\n（梁天琦，2016）"},{"pid":"0c4db4e3bc0af9572fc15a06f14d95f299dffd18","tid":669422,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"屌, 睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2a863e0e4028138c57f17db8df8de4d4520e8e","tid":669422,"uid":5843,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0c4db4e3bc0af9572fc15a06f14d95f299dffd18","tid":669422,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"屌, 睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f2b9c7643aa759672d594e3b1ae1f7ca265388","tid":669422,"uid":67485,"like":5,"dislike":83,"score":-78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:32:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb167971c0a54222ec56e0f4b9efd66a443e07e6","tid":669422,"uid":5843,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啲五毛勤力到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd429f38157f402b3a61e84b21f649f3e86c33da","tid":669422,"uid":107210,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"d3f2b9c7643aa759672d594e3b1ae1f7ca265388","tid":669422,"uid":67485,"like":5,"dislike":83,"score":-78,"citedBy":2,"replyTim